title: 2016 Appalachian Trail Thru Hikers AWOL Guides
description:
The 2016 update of the Thru Hikers Companion and AWOL guides, plus various maps and information for the Appalachian Trail. 

Includes:

2016 Thru-Hikers Companion (at_guide_thc_2016.pdf)
2016 AWOL Northbound Guide (at_guide_awol_2016_nobo.pdf)
2016 AWOL Southbound Guide (at_guide_awol_2016_sobo.pdf)
ALDHA latest newsletter for AT (aldha_2015-2016_winter.pdf}
ALDHA important links (aldha-companion-online.htm)
ATC latest updates for the trail (atc_updates_march2016.pdf)
Map of entire AT (at-map.pdf)
Trailhead parking places (at_parking.pdf)
Profile/Elevation maps of the AT (at-profiles.pdf)
AT list of known shuttle and transportation services (at_shuttles_2016.pdf)
Map of AT (at-strip-map.pdf)
ALDHA 2016 Brochure (brochure16.pdf)
GIS Data for the whole AT (gisdata_AT_Centerline_12-23-2014.zip)
GIS Data for the parking locations (gisdata_at_parking.zip)
GIS Data for the shelter locations (gisdata_AT_Shelters.zip)
List of commonly used trail abbreviations  (trail_abbreviations.pdf)
Page with topographic map links of the US/AT (USA_Topo_Maps.html)


If you found this guide useful - please donate to the ATC or ALDHA, and keep the trail beautiful!
